title: An Introduction to Cricut Explore One
description: An Introduction to Cricut Explore One
transcripts: Introducing Cricut Explore One a design and cut system that is so easy to use you'll be making amazing projects in just minutes. Cricut Explore One is incredibly versatile you can use it for just about any project you dream up. It cuts a wide variety of materials from paper to vinyl and iron on, it even cuts thicker materials like leather and felt and look even the most intricate cuts are so clean because crickets free design space software is so intuitive anyone can design and cut like an expert. Plus its cloud-based so you can start a project on your iPad while you're out and about and then finish it up on your computer when you get home. Cricut Explore One lets you cut your own designs and fonts for free just upload your own images and then add them to your project and start cutting. If you don't have your own designs don't worry you can always browse through the 50,000 images in the Cricut image library images start at just 99 cents and the image library is always growing. You'll be amazed as to how often you'll be making projects, a personalized baby shower gift, a vinyl quote for your wall or a Valentine for your sweetheart it's easy-peasy to design your own projects from scratch or you can make it even faster by selecting from hundreds of make it now projects. Make it now projects are already designed and ready to go in just one click so you can make projects in just minutes with Cricut Explore One you'll go from inspiration to creation everywhere.
